1
00:00:08,060 --> 00:00:08,740
(Mu Yinan,)

2
00:00:08,740 --> 00:00:10,180
(Regret Inn)

3
00:00:10,180 --> 00:00:10,820
(do you think)

4
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:13,003
(love will disappear all of a sudden?)

5
